MESSAGE.value: set-property macro
Merged origin/master
Refactoring - Added component as an argument to event handlers - Moved TestUI to test directory - Added functions for error generation
Documentation update and Codox generation
Removed IUDataStore protocol - component access now simple functions on a UI - added FormAndTableUI example - various re-naming and re-factoring
Added MarginInfo construction - Major refactor of component configuration
Addition of RxClojure integration - buttonClick and valueChange observers
Addition of RxClojure integration - commit and consume-for operations
Improved/fixed table column configuration - can now accept all setColumnXXX setters on parent table - Renamed and extended FormAndTableUI -> Sampler - Minor config refactoring
User.clj updates
Added ProgressBar - config gen tweaking
Added TODOs
Added working ProgressBar to Sampler
Added nul representation to Sampler and TestUI
Better code styling for ui build trees
Fixed missing function
Form builder now takes arguments similar to Panel - new public lookup - componentNamed - refactoring
Improved Background Task in Sampler
Added MenuBar and MenuItem/Separator - Reforming for new indentation

Reworked field binding, added -main function, refactoring - Fields now bind with :bindTo config option - Added -main to run UI's in jetty server - Reworked create-widget to return just widget when no children
Removed old event handling config options
Now BETA, CHANGELOG updated
Added interactive cmd-line run, addStyleNamed config option

Various additions/refactoring - Form vaiidation: new :addValidations config option, plus FunctionalValidator type - Added missing (window) builder - Added (with-ui-access) Rx operator - Added main run() function to interactivey run examples - Added utils, updated Sampler
